      & D\ar [ur, "\operatorname *{Lan}_K F"']\makebox [0pt][l]{,}
      \ar [Rightarrow, from=F, to=2-2, "\eta "]
    \end {tikzcd}


 that is universal in that for any other pair D\xrightarrow {G} E and
  F\xrightarrow {\gamma } GK, \gamma  factors uniquely through \eta : 




